For basic examples, you only need libqt4-dev
sudo apt-get install libqt4-dev

More information here: http://www.zetcode.com/gui/qt4/introduction/

To build project, use:

qmake -project
qmake
make

no need of a custom makefile.

QT5 errors when QApplication is not recognized:
to avoid this, add the following line to the .pro file:
QT += widgets

To find QT version installed, run the following:
qmake --version
